rComments: Once you figure out exactly what he's looking for on the homework you will be able to do well on them, and the exams, which are set up like longer versions of the homework.  He gives out a ton of extra credit. So take advantage of all opportunities.

Ben is extremely pompous, and can listen to his own voice for hours on end. His students, however, are put to sleep within minutes. Class doesn't get challenging until the end, and even so, most people don't come to lecture since Ben can't seem to teach anything. Pointless class and Ben is an awful TA. Would NEVER take again if I had the choice!!!!
